com.jfx

Class ObjectVisibility

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jfx.ObjectVisibility

  • public class ObjectVisibility
extends Object
    Timeframes where object may be shown. Used in ObjectSet() function to set OBJPROP_TIMEFRAMES property.
